In a message dated 3/3/04 12:32:55 PM, erikanunn@... writes:

<< I am not receiving individual emails to erikanunn@.... >>

The list has been really quiet. The only thing I know is to go in and change
your setting, and then change it back. A little "reboot" bit. If you change
it to no mail or digest and then back in a bit maybe that will do it. Or
maybe you're find and the list is sleeping.

Sandra
